system2.direct_addressing::SendNoteToTes.name: system2.direct_addressing::SendNoteToTest
system2.direct_addressing::SendNoteToTes.description: Tests that a note by actor A is delivered to an actor B if A addresses the note to B.

system2.follow_receive::FollowReceiveTes.name: system2.follow_receive::FollowReceiveTest
system2.follow_receive::FollowReceiveTes.description: Tests that actors on two different Fediverse Nodes can follow each other and a follower receives the followed account's posts.

system2.like_single_hop::LikeTest.name: system2.like_single_hop::LikeTest
system2.like_single_hop::LikeTest.description:
Tests that actor B can like a note by actor A on a different Fediverse Node
    and both see the Like. Unlike works the reverse.

    https://github.com/fediverse-devnet/feditest-tests-fediverse/issues/149

system2.preserve_links::PreserveBlockquo.name: system2.preserve_links::PreserveBlockquoteTest
system2.preserve_links::PreserveBlockquo.description: Make sure that all hyperlinks in a note are still present on the receiving node. They may be rearranged.

system2.reply_single_hop::ReplyTest.name: system2.reply_single_hop::ReplyTest
system2.reply_single_hop::ReplyTest.description:
Tests that actor B can reply to a note by actor A on a different Fediverse Node and both see the reply.

    https://github.com/fediverse-devnet/feditest-tests-fediverse/issues/128

system2.update_single_hop::UpdateTest.name: system2.update_single_hop::UpdateTest
system2.update_single_hop::UpdateTest.description:
Tests that actor B's copy of a note by actor A is correctly updated when A updates it on a different Fediverse Node.

    https://github.com/fediverse-devnet/feditest-tests-fediverse/issues/151
